     You can also cast spells via the keyboard:

     To cast spell 1: <1> key.
     To cast spell 2: <2> key.
     To cast spell 3: <3> key.
     To cast spell 4: <4> key.
     To cast spell 5: <5> key.
     To cast spell 6: <6> key.
     To cast spell 7: <7> key.
     To cast spell 8: <8> key.

     Note: If you hold down the <ALT> key while pressing the spell key, you will cast the spells on yourself or on your nearest enemy (for various damage-dealing spells).
